\c 10
\s Kukumbira kuti vakaipa vaparadzwe
\p
\v 1 Munomirirei kure, Jehovha? Munovandire\add i\add* panguva dzedambudziko?
\v 2 Wakaipa pakuzvikudza anoshusha murombo. Ngavabatwe mumazano avakafunga.
\v 3 Nokuti wakaipa anozvirumbidza pazvishuvo zvemweya wake, ndokuropafadza muchivi, anozvidza Jehovha.
\v 4 Wakaipa nekuzvikudza kwechiso chake \add anoti\add*: Ha\add ndi\add*bvunzi; hakuna Mwari \add mu\add*mirangariro yake yese.
\v 5 Nzira dzake dzakasimba nenguva dzese; mitongo yenyu yakakwirira iri kure naye; vavengi vake vese anovafuridza.
\v 6 Anoti mumoyo make: Handingazungunuswi; nokuti pamazera nepamazera handingavi pakarema.
\v 7 Muromo wake uzere kutuka nekunyengera neutsotsi; pasi perurimi rwake pane kutadza neuipi.
\v 8 Anogara panzvimbo dzekuvandira dzemisha; panzvimbo dzakavanda anouraya asina mhosva; meso ake anotarisa asina mubatsiri pachivande.
\v 9 Anovandira pakavanda seshumba pagara rayo; anovanda kubata murombo; anobata murombo paanomukwevera mumumbure wake.
\v 10 Anyangira, anokambaira, kuti varombo vawiswe pamwe nevanesimba vake.
\v 11 Anoti mumoyo make: Mwari wakanganwa; anovanza chiso chake, haangatongooni narinhi.
\p
\v 12 Simukai Jehovha; Mwari simudzai ruoko rwenyu; regai kukanganwa vanotambudzika.
\v 13 Sei wakaipa achizvidza Mwari? Anoti mumoyo make: Haungabvunzi?
\v 14 Maona henyu; nokuti imwi munotarira chakaipa nedambudziko, kukuisa muruoko rwako; murombo anozvipa kwamuri; imwi muri mubatsiri wenherera.
\v 15 Vhunai ruoko rwewakaipa; newakashata, tsvakai kuipa kwake, kusvika musingawani.
\v 16 Jehovha ndiye Mambo nekusingaperi-peri; vahedheni vakaparara munyika yake.
\v 17 Jehovha, makanzwa chishuvo chevanyoro; muchasimbisa moyo wavo, muchaita nzeve yenyu inzwe;
\v 18 kutonga nherera neanomanikidzwa, kuti munhu wepanyika asachivhundusa.